[h4 
	" Moving fleet
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"Fleet speed is variable in 1-5 dot/frame. 
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"The diagonal moving is 1.4 times faster than horz/vert.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Basically, fleet moves by spd5, at entering the planet, down speed to 2.
	$LF
]p
